                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant K</hi> 7). I produce a certificate of Willis's conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted March</hi> 1847, <hi rend="italic">and confined six months</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
